transform_def.name: designed10
transform_def.string: let r = 1 / length(p_in) a = atan2(p_in.x * p_in.y * sinh(p_in.x), abs(p_in.y / cos(p_in.x))) a2 = atan2(length(p_in), p_in.x * p_in.y) z = abs(cos((a * a2) * (p_in.x * (tan(p_in.y) + sin(p_in.x)))) * (a2)) con1 = z < r con2 = z > r in (if if fill > 0.0 then con1 else con2 then p_in else vec2(0.0)) * weight
